ezSynergy

OSX GUI Wrapper for Synergy (http://synergy-foss.org/)

Michael Clifford <michael@suitepotato.com>
http://suitepotato.com
http://twitter.com/suiteblog

Synergy icons modified for this project by Chris Melby <me@chrismelby.com>

